  <brief_title>Prevalence of Wound Healing Disturbances in Geriatric Inpatients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Prevalence of Wound Healing Disturbances in Geriatric Inpatients With Specific Focus on Malnutrition, Other Nutritional Parameters and the Frailty Syndrome</official_title>
